                <span class="">Manis Mizrachi</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#mizrachiM" start="1328.143" end="x">No, I learned it quite alone. There was a friend of mine who went to the school . . . and I learned . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="1332.854" end="x">And learned it alone. Now what do you plan to do in the future?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Manis Mizrachi</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#mizrachiM" start="1336.420" end="x">I am studying now; I am studying radio.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="1339.432" end="x">Where, at the <a class="term" href="#vothG_ort">ORT</a>?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Manis Mizrachi</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#mizrachiM" start="1340.727" end="x">No, quite alone, I am training myself.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="1344.011" end="x">All right.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
